cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper deals with incorporating anatomical prior knowledge into CNNs for image analysis tasks such as image enhancement and segmentation. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The proposed regularisation model is a learning-based technique, which also falls under the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category. The paper also deals with multi-modal data sets, which falls under the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category. Finally, the paper demonstrates how the learnt deep models can be used for classification, which falls under the neural networks (cs.NE) sub-category.
